'From Squeak3.9 of 7 November 2006 [latest update: #7067] on 23 January 2008 at 7:11:34 pm'!"Change Set:		MenuMorph-addAllFromFIx-MUDate:			23 January 2008Author:			Masashi UmezawaMenuMorph>>addAllFrom: should set default target to each menu items if they do not have their own targets.By this patch, Mantis bug:0005297 can be solved."!!MenuMorph methodsFor: 'construction' stamp: 'mu 1/23/2008 18:52'!addAllFrom: aMenuMorph 	aMenuMorph submorphs		do: [:each | 			(each isKindOf: MenuItemMorph)				ifTrue: [self						add: each contents						target: (each target ifNil: [self defaultTarget])						selector: each selector						argumentList: each arguments].			(each isKindOf: MenuLineMorph)				ifTrue: [self addLine]] ! !